description: You’re invited to come enjoy an authentic New Orleans experience on the streets of Cleveland, courtesy of Zydeco Bistro and their delicious selection of Creole & Cajun cuisine. This eye-catching yellow truck is owned and operated by Chef Johnny, who hails from Southern Louisiana where he built quite an impressive culinary career. Now he’s bringing those beautiful bayou flavors to Northeast Ohio. His menu includes many Nola favorites like Cajun Jambalaya, Andouille Sausage Po’ Boys, Crispy Gulf Shrimp Baskets, and many more. Each bite is like sweet accordion music to your appetite. Make any day feel just like Mardi Gras by going to eat at Zydeco Bistro!
name: Zydeco Bistro
